{"tid":849403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立　中國想　海上封鎖　經濟制裁　根本做不成","createTime":"2018-10-05T16:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T20:45:47.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0538e37b77dba2fa75bd9216dfcf3b1a267bbea","tid":849403,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/a.472253396306953/800782040120752/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fphotos%2Fa.472253396306953%2F800782040120752%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=ooEBiEgNkjqGn8ra58NECzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ca11ecd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/photos/a.472253396306953/800782040120752/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n講海上封鎖根本白痴。海上定點不動的船根本是活靶，何況中國也沒有那麼多海軍船。海洋就像一個球場，船隻就像球場上的人，是蚊牛之比，周邊國家都不賣你帳，球員人數少根本守不了人數多。何況以前柏林被紅色陸地包圍都一樣死不了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156329901027357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156329901027357&d=ooEBiEgNkjqGn8ra58NECzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=299fe33c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156329901027357</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n世界有多少國家能自給自足？可能除了美國。<br />\n世界上能做有效的經濟制裁的，可能只有美國&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n問題是，為甚麼別人要聯合你的經濟制裁？<br />\n經濟制裁的情況其實有留意現代新聞，近乎美國專利。<br />\n北韓、古巴之類，共通點是與美國為敵、與自由世界為敵&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.plurk.com/p/lawk4i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plurk.com%2Fp%2Flawk4i&d=ooEBiEgNkjqGn8ra58NECzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=12b923d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.plurk.com/p/lawk4i</a><br />\n<br />\nまる@馬娘世界一:<br />\n就像美國要經濟制裁還是得要跟其他國家商量一樣，其他國家不配合也不能大剌剌的把別人封鎖"},{"pid":"5cd9e22f36e6c45e90c1d4cf9eb8dc22c3922799","tid":849403,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T19:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4193ea008b42cd54bbcef43ee8e97ed2d37a797","tid":849403,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T19:30:48.000Z","msg":"而家香港獨立最大嘅障礙就係香港人夠膽有獨立嘅念頭"},{"pid":"46b3c28d4ba3118463f741ae6913001d6c9619c6","tid":849403,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"香港班泛民左膠先係最大障礙"}]}